Package com.capgemini.cobigen.api.exception

  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    CobiGenRuntimeException
    A technical runtime exception indicating an unexpected error cause.
    InputReaderException
    Exception to indicate that an InputReader encountered a problem while parsing input content.
    InvalidConfigurationException
    Occurs if the configuration could not be parsed successfully
    MergeException
    This Exception indicates a problem while merging.
    NotYetSupportedException
    States that any logic has been triggered, which is currently not supported.
    PluginNotAvailableException
    Raised if a plugin is configured in one of the configurations which cannot be found.
    UnknownExpressionException
    Occurs if a variable expression in the configuration xml is unknown
